{"tid":333991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【似曾相識】非洲中心主義","createTime":"2017-07-24T10:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-24T12:11:24.000Z","uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"927382172b3c296a37ac255a4daefee0b7658abb","tid":333991,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"非洲中心主義（afrocentrism）可以看做是非洲裔美國人對白人主導社會的反抗。這一理論試圖最大程度地貶低歐洲文化對非洲人生活的影響，強調歷史上獨立的非洲文明，及其輝煌的科技成果。這一理論以撒哈拉以南的非洲為中心解釋世界歷史，並認為在此發生的偉大成就最終被阿拉伯人和白人摧毀。"},{"pid":"b3911816bf5ff148cab15a18b919cc737d6dbfd9","tid":333991,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"好似有講過，古埃及法老，其實係黑人。"},{"pid":"95e9a4cd9e9ce8ffe6d645af3812747040a5b44f","tid":333991,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e38ca6613a703465f40a7edf47500aa8a9b60f5","tid":333991,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T12:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}